Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:30.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ナルト）ヨタ！　頼む。\Nやめてくれってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:32.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:36.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！！\N《サクラ：ナルト！》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サクラちゃん？》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:42.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,《あんた　ヨタって言ったわよね？\Nそっちにも来てるの？》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,《そっちって…　サクラちゃんの\Nところにもいるのかよ？》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:47.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,《シカマル：サクラどころじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:50.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺たちのところにも\Nキバのところにも…》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:53.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,《キバ：あぁ…\N派手にやってくれてるぜ》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:57.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヨタが４人…》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:00.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,《チョウジ：ヨタ　怒ってるのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:02.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから　みんなのところに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:05.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,僕たちのせいで\N死んじゃったから…》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:07.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヨタは　幽霊じゃねぇぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:09.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,穢土転生で操られてんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:11.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,しっかりしろ　チョウジ》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:13.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ちょっと　待てよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,穢土転生って　影分身みたいに\Nそんなにいっぱい→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:17.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,よみがえらせることが\Nできんのかよ？》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.46,0:01:19.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,《これまでは　なかったが…》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:23.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,《俺が　相手してんのは\N間違いなくヨタだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:26.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃあ\Nみんなのところにいるのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:29.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの　白いヤツかも\Nしれねえってばよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:31.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,白ゼツか。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:33.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,本物じゃないってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:36.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも　この雪はヨタの…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:39.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや　本体が術をかけてりゃ\N問題ねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:43.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,というより　ヨタを操ってる誰かだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんな　きっとそいつらは\Nヨタじゃねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:50.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから\Nみんなが苦しむことなんかない。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:52.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,痛みは　俺が引き受ける。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:57.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから　倒しちまってくれ。\Nニセモンのヨタを！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:02:00.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:02.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ヨタ）フフフッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:04.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,ごめんな　ヨタ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:56.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,超倍化の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,影真似の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,ニセモンとはいえよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,いくぜ　赤丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:52.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,ざけんなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,はぁ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:10.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:21.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,《あのとき俺たちは\Nヨタを助けようとした。　けど…》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,((また　１人か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:30.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃねえよ。　６人と１匹だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなで来ちゃった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,なっ…　あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前ら！\N人んちにズカズカと入るんじゃ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,何言ってんの。\N今まで寂しそうにしてたくせに。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,ったく　いい天気だってのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,部屋の中いると　ますます誰も\N寄りつかなくな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん？　雨が降ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,（２人）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺たちで　ヨタを奪い返すんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:30.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,どこから来た？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,どこの里だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:37.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,私　わからないよ…　難しいこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:41.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,優しいこと言ってよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:46.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,どこから来た？　どこの里だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,埒が明かないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:56.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,手荒になる前に\N一度　三代目にお越し願おうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:20.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,《幻術？　いや…》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,ギャーッ　ハハハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:31.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,コラ！　やめろ！\N下りてこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:35.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,バーカ！　誰が下りるかってぇの！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:39.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺は　うずまきナルト！\N忍者だってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,（火影）なに！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:45.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤツは　問題の少年と一緒にいた\Nアカデミー生徒の１人です。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:51.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,捕まえられるもんなら\N捕まえてみろってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:55.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,里中の忍者　みんなこ～い！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:59.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,待て　この悪ガキが！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:02.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,天気雨…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:05.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,まったく！\Nなんてバチ当たりなヤツだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:09.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,三代目様の顔岩は\Nそりゃあ　もうメチャクチャらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうらしいな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:14.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,この里で暮らしていながら\Nなぜ　そんなことができるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,アタッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,（２人）おっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:24.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,何か見た？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:28.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや…　ハハッ　気のせいだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:36.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,お願いだから　もう助けてよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:40.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,うっ…　うぅ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,影真似の術　成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:55.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,（みんな）ヨタ！　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,おい！\N大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:03.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,（みんな）ヒヒヒヒッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,やっぱりすごいよ　シカマル！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:10.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,大人の忍者に\N術をかけちゃうなんて。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,（いの）アンタ　ひょっとして天才？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:15.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや　まだまだひよっこだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,チッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,動くな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:29.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,里の利益をおびやかす者は\N子供といえど　容赦はしない。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,コイツは　スパイかもしれないんだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,ふざけんな！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:43.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,コイツは…　ヨタは　そんなんじゃねえ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:49.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタは…　俺の…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺の初めてできた友達だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,友達…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,うっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:25.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,わ…　私の…　友達！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,逃げるってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,深ぇぞ　この川。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも　ここを越えないと…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう追っ手が向かってるはずよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,水の上が渡れたら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:17.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,（キバ）行くっきゃねえよ！\N（赤丸）ワンワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:22.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,行こう。　ヨタを自由なところへ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,ガハッ…。\Nナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:07.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,チョウジ！　シカマル！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,プハッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:23.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,（みんな）ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:30.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハア…　ハア…　ゴホッ　ゴホッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:34.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハア…　ハア…　ハア…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…　ありがとな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヨタ！！))
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:54.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,((みんな：ヨタ！　ヨタ！　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ？\Nヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:07.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,しっかりして！\N（チョウジ）平気？　寒くない？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！　もう　大丈夫だから。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。\Nしっかりしなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,（赤丸）クゥーン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:23.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,よかったね　みんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:27.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう　大丈夫だからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:32.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前がだよ！\Nしっかりしてくれよ。　なぁ　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:36.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,私は　もう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダメだよ。　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:43.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,ごめん。　俺が　ムチャしなけりゃ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺のせいだ。\Nクゥーン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:49.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,もっと　いい手があったはず…\Nなのによ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:54.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！\Nヨタ…　ごめん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,お別れだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:05.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,何　言ってんだよ！？\Nこれからも　俺たちは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:09.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,私は　みんなのこと　忘れない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:15.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも　みんなは\N私のこと　忘れるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:17.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,バカなこと　言ってんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:22.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,忘れるわけ　ないだろ！\N（シカマルたち）そうだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:31.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,忘れなきゃ　つらいよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:40.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…　俺は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヨタ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:51.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,《そして　俺たちは　ヨタを忘れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:55.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,楽しかった　すべてを。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:59.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなと友達だったことも。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:03.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,俺は　ひとりぼっちに戻った》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…　俺は忘れたくなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:15.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前とのこと　忘れるくらいなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:19.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前を死なせた後悔の中で\N生きてたほうが　よっぽど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:23.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう一度…　もう一度　ヨタを→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:27.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,あんな目に\Nあわせなきゃなんねえのかよ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:37.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,耐えられるわけ　ないだろ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:16:00.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ナルト…　私だよ　ヨタだよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヨタ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:09.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ナルトと私の秘密の糸電話だよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:13.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,《これなら\N穢土転生の術者に聞かれずに…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ナルト…　アンタの頭の中のその声！》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヨタ！》\N《２人：ヨタ！》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヨタじゃねえか！》\N《ワン！》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:25.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サクラ　シカマル　いの　チョウジ　キバ　赤丸》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ごめん　ごめん…　ごめんね》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,《なんで謝るの？》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:35.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,《俺たちは　お前を\N助けることができなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:38.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,死なせちまったんだ。\Nだから　みんな…》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ナルトもね　みんなもね→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:44.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,気にすることなんか\N何もないんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:48.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,だって　私はね\Nナルトたちに会ったとき→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:50.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう　死んでたんだもん》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:56.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,《穢土転生でよみがえって\Nそれで　ナルトたちに会ったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:17:01.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう死んでたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:07.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,私は　天気を操る不思議な\N力を持った一族に生まれて→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:13.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,天気売りを商売にして\N里から里へ旅して歩いた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:20.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,私　一族のなかでも　特に\N天気使いがうまかったんだよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:31.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,《でもね　生まれつき\N体が弱くってね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,死んじゃったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:40.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,死んだんだけど\N呼び止められちゃった》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,((キャーッ！))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:06.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,《カブト：ヨタ　役立てよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:11.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヨタ：蛇とメガネがね\N穢土転生のテストだっていって→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:15.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトたちの里に\N私を置いていったんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,私はね　悲しかった》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:21.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:26.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サクラ：ホントに　ごめんね。\N一緒にいてあげられなくて》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:29.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ううん　謝ることないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:34.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,あのね　私　生きてるとき\Nつらくて　つらくて。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:37.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,どこにいても\Nずっと　ひとりぼっちだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:42.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,でもね　死んでから\Nひとりぼっちじゃなくなった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:47.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなに会って\Nホントに楽しかったんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:51.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの川で　また\Nよみがえってしまったけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:57.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,あれからまた１人で　死にながら\N生き続けてきたけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:01.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなとの思い出があるから\Nつらくなんかなかった》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:09.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,《それに　こんなかたちだけど\Nみんなに　また会えた。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,大きくなったね　ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:16.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,サクラも　シカマルも　いのも　チョウジも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:20.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,キバも　赤丸も元気そうだ》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:24.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ　だったら　楽しもうぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:27.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,穢土転生なんて関係ねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:35.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,前みたいに　一緒に　喜んで\N怒って　悲しんで　楽しむんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,《なに　これは…》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:46.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,コンコンコン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:51.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,《嬉しいよ　私は楽しいよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ナルト　みんな　ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,楽しいまま　私はいくよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:03.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,今度はね　みんな私のこと\N忘れちゃやだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,覚えてておくれよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:08.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダメだ　ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,《ヨタ：これで思い残すことはない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:16.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,ホントに死ねる。　バイバイ　ナルト　みんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:21.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,明日も晴れますように》
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:25.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヨタ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:39.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,（ヨタ）フフフッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:40.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,皆様　お変わりございませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.08,0:22:42.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,美空ひばりです。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:46.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,では最後まで\Nごゆっくりお楽しみください。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:53.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,（宮本）『木曜８時のコンサート\N名曲！にっぽんの歌』。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:55.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,２時間スペシャル。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:28.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:29.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:31.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:35.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:35.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naruto?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:37.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sakura?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:41.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you just say "Yota"?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:42.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he there too?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:46.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean, "there too"?{\i0}\N{\i1}He's with you also?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only Sakura!{\i0}\N{\i1}But with us too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Including Kiba!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:53.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh boy… He's really going at it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are four Yotas?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if Yota is angry at us…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:05.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe that's why he came to each of us.{\i0}\N{\i1}Because we let him die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yota is not a ghost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was reanimated{\i0}\N{\i1}and is being controlled!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:10.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get your act together, Choji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:12.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hold on a sec!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:15.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So with Reanimation,{\i0}\N{\i1}you can be resurrected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:17.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}lots of times like Shadow Clones?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not until now…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.40,0:01:22.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm positive it's Yota I'm facing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:28.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means, all of you could{\i0}\N{\i1}be seeing that white guy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:31.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, White Zetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's not the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:36.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But this snow is Yota's…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.36,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the real one is\Nperforming the jutsu, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:42.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say,\Nthe one controlling Yota.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone… These guys aren't Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:48.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't need to feel guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:52.94,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take on your guilt! So…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.32,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them down…\NTake down the Yota impostors!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:03.86,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yota…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:39.26,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lingering Snow{\i0}\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Expansion Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Possession Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is an impostor…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Akamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:20.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back then, we tried to save Yota.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.05,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm alone again…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.26,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's six of us plus one dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We all came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What—?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:39.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! You can't just\Nwalk in uninvited…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:43.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no way to talk.\NYou looked so lonely right up 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.42,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez… It's so nice outside…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:49.05,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay cooped up like this,\Nno one will want to…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:51.92,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.42,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.09,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Yota?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.34,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get Yota back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.26,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.09,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What village?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:37.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't…know…\Nabout complicated stuff…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me easy questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from? What village?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.34,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We should ask Lord Third to come\Nbefore things get more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it genjutsu…? No…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.42,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:35.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots! As if I'd do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:38.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Naruto Uzumaki! I'm a ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.22,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:43.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the students\Nfrom the Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,who was with the boy in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All the ninja in the village!\NCome and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:58.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,– That damned brat!\N– Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.34,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sun showers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:05.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a pain in the butt…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:07.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Lord Third's\NMountainside Image
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.22,english,,0000,0000,0000,,is badly damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.22,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives in our village.\NHow could he do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:22.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.51,0:08:25.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:29.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:36.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I beg you. Let me go…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Possession Jutsu complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:54.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yota! Hey!\N– Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.34,english,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hey! Yota!\N– Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:07.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru, you're amazing, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:09.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a jutsu on grown-up ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.05,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you some kind of genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope… He's still wet behind the ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.22,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who threatens\Nthe welfare of the village
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.09,english,,0000,0000,0000,,will be treated harshly,\Neven if they are children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He could be a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.42,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.34,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota isn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.42,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:52.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota is…the first friend…\NI've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.76,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:25.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… My friend…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:43.59,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.09,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This river is deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.72,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to cross it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably coming\Nafter us already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:15.09,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could walk on water…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:21.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go someplace\Nwhere Yota can be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.84,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
